TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT KSRB300_COUNT_SUM.RAC_NB ,KSRB300_COUNT_SUM.RBAT_ID ,KSRB300_COUNT_SUM.CG_NB ,KSRB300_COUNT_SUM.INV_CCYY ,KSRB300_COUNT_SUM.INV_QTR ,KSRB300_COUNT_SUM.LCM_CD ,KSRB300_COUNT_SUM.SUM_LCM_CD ,KSRB300_COUNT_SUM.CLM_CNT_TYP_CD ,KSRB300_COUNT_SUM.PMT_SYS_ELIG_CD ,KSRB300_COUNT_SUM.RBAT_CLM_CNT ,KSRB300_COUNT_SUM.SUBM_CLM_CNT ,KSRB300_COUNT_SUM.INSRT_TS ,KSRB300_COUNT_SUM.LAST_UPDT_TS ,KSRB300_COUNT_SUM.LAST_UPDT_PGM_NM FROM $$MVS_DB2_OWNER.KSRB300_COUNT_SUM KSRB300_COUNT_SUM WHERE KSRB300_COUNT_SUM.LAST_UPDT_TS > $$LAST_UPDT_TS AND KSRB300_COUNT_SUM.CLM_CNT_TYP_CD <> '10'
